               <h5>Design Motivations</h5>
               <p class="para1">
  The severity of cardiovascular disease is beyond imagination in China, with over 290 million patients reported in the year of 2014. The resource of public health care is limited for these people. If their conditions are not highly dangerous, most of them will still go to work and not be able to monitor heart conditions on a day-to-day basis. This fact drives me to realize the solution of a mobile-based ECG device.
</p>

